Experience complete privacy and comfort in our luxurious accommodation. Amazing Hotel

We stayed at the hotel for 7 nights and loved it! The location is very central (short walk to all the shops) and very close to the beach. The beds were very comfortable and the breakfast buffet was excellent. The hotel staff were very helpful with advice and recommendations. We definitely want to stay here again, when we are back in Palma.
